precis:
Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1066) by making it
mandatory to fortify flour and enriched pasta with folic acid and by
harmonizing the Canadian vitamin and mineral enrichment requirements for
flour and enriched pasta with U.S. standards.
